<aside>POST /api/hrm/people/{id}/timeoff</aside>

<p>Create new Time off Policy.</p>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Attribute</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>name</td>
<td>Name of the Time off policy</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>total_timeoff</td>
<td>total number of timeoff</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>policy_effective_date</td>
<td>policy effective from date</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>policy_renew_type</td>
<td>time of renewal of policy</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>day_hours</td>
<td>total work hours per day</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>timeoff_interval</td>
<td>number of days after which new hire can apply for leave</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<h4 id="returns">Returns</h4>

<p>If the call succeeds, the <a href="#time-off-policy-object">timeoff policy</a> object is returned with all the information about the timeoff policy.</p>

<h3 id="delete-time-off-policy">Delete Time Off Policy</h3>

<aside>DELETE api/hrm/organization/settings/timeoff-policy/{id}</aside>
